      "content": "but the \"political power\" thing feels like a cover story. like, look at the way the angles of the streets change as you move outward from the center. there's a specific frequency to the spacing that reminded me of occult geometry used in ancient ritual sites. if you look at the way those diagonal lines intersect with the grid, it's almost like they're meant to channel or trap something. why would \"political unity\" require such a specific, esoteric geometric signature? it feels way more intentional than just making a symbol of government.",
